column5: I got a nice surprise on my last outing to Simcoe. It was released to surprise some one else.
Nice fish, No lakers for me last season good to know that we still have some left.
Oh look, A small one,,,,LOL  Nice going jimmer .
Nice trout!! I love those bigger fish... the bigger the hook jaw,the bigger the fish
Nice fish Jimmer must of been a hell of a fight
I try every year to catch a big Lake Trout. I will someday. Pictures like this keep my dream alive. Nice catch. Glad you also released it.
